---
title: Saucy Spanish-Style Beef Meatballs with Garlicky Couscous & Parsley
description: These pork meatballs are bursting with bright flavours, coated in a veggie-filled tomato sauce. Sitting atop a bed of
garlic couscous to soak up all of that goodness, what more could you possibly want?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
